org.eclipse.january.dataset

Class BooleanIterator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.january.dataset.IndexIterator
      • org.eclipse.january.dataset.BooleanIterator
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    BooleanBroadcastIterator, BooleanContiguousIterator, BooleanNullIterator

    public abstract class BooleanIterator
extends IndexIterator
    Base class for boolean iterators for pairs of dataset where the second dataset could be broadcast to the first and is used to select where {IndexIterator.hasNext() returns true. An optional third dataset can specify the output. For speed, there are public members.
